### 8. Import Statements

**File: `internal/ui/model_view.go`**

No new imports needed (already has fmt).

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Color interpolation uses proper RGB blending
- [ ] Color palette cycles every 8 seconds smoothly
- [ ] All four columns use consistent animated styling
- [ ] Running agents have bold, prominent status dots
- [ ] Failed agents have bright red indicators
- [ ] Confirm view has prominent "READY?" text
- [ ] Loading states feel responsive and engaging
- [ ] Typography hierarchy is clear (titles vs content)
- [ ] All effects are subtle, not distracting
- [ ] Performance remains smooth
- [ ] Tests pass

## Notes

- Glow effects are kept simple - true multi-layer borders require more complex lipgloss compositing
- Color cycling makes the UI feel more alive without being flashy
- Agent status improvements provide clear visual feedback
- Confirm view enhancements create satisfying "final selection" moment
- Loading animations make wait times feel shorter
- All effects should be tested in both light and dark terminal modes

## Dependencies

- Depends on: bb-cj8-lockin-flash (needs animation system and lock-in mechanics)

## Completes

- This completes the visual polish work for bb-cj8
- Parent task bb-cj8 can be closed after this and all dependent tickets are complete

